<a href='/eq/view_profile?user.id=98953'  class="auth_text"  style="font-weight:bold;" >	
<span style='color:#330066;'>Lluianae</span> <img src='http://eq2players.station.sony.com/images/community/forumimages/leaf.gif' border=0 alt=''> </a>
