			>
			In fact one could effectively camp more than 5 25/25s (Stonewarden and
shard, I haven't counted the slots they can go in), as well as the 30
aug from Valdoon (which is dead easy to do) things like that on top of
whats already mentioned, its true AC is far easier to achieve than
getting all the super high hp raid augs, of which are subject to your
guilds distribution system and not exp group rules.<br>
<br>
There is a point where extra may seem pointless, you've already
achieved the basic level of survivability, but I know it can and does
help, its just tradition that when this happens you should focus on HP
more, and thats where being balanced comes into play. But since this is
a thread about mitigation, I thought I'd stick to the AC side /shrug.<br>
